		{
			"id":"8e7e150c5e1d23f5",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"用言：形容词，形容动词，动词，助动词，小句子",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":70,
			"y":-469,
			"width":460,
			"height":60,
			"color":"2"
		},
		{
			"id":"bcdccc133b90103a",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"形容词",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":-560,
			"y":1540,
			"width":260,
			"height":60
		},
		{
			"id":"c6cbdc3e603ddf0e",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"连体形（な），终止形（だ）只有形容动词不同。两种词都没有命令形。",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":-560,
			"y":1660,
			"width":260,
			"height":100
		},
